By":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去電視台睇下音樂節目好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩條件入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常都係cd，音源啊，會員證個啲咁上下既野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶隻CD去就入得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地排音樂節目要分優次架，例如你齊cd，音源，官方一期會員都為之第一順位，每少一樣野就跌一個順位，得cd既話可能排到最後都唔出奇，如果個日只係比50人入，頭一順位有30人，二順位有20人，你排三順位就入唔到架啦。不過通常預錄得cd都入到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生放送既話就算齊曬就未必入到，除非係你追個隊係大勢同個日既一位後補咁就有機會會放多啲人入去囉，不過通常預錄都睇到既，至少我去咁多次，次次都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0d5e8baadfbdb1258d89ba86508ff9a5432525","tid":16570,"uid":11907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>韓國咁悶真係無咩好玩，追開邊團啊，去下佢地公司附近行下可能隨時會撞到都唔頂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住去CUBE YG同JYP撞下 仲有啲細公司想去睇下但係驚太僻唔識去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比個貼士你啊，去公司附近coffee shop分分鐘有驚喜啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一個人去？其實韓國gps好準下架，開住google map就唔會咁易蕩失路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔敢自己一個去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕，韓國都相對上都係安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7933bed140727e6a1fe52ce783f0f21f53643788","tid":16570,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去電視台睇下音樂節目好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br /